title: 2011 Wichita mayoral election
text: The 2011 Wichita mayoral election took place on April 5, 2011, to elect the <a href="List%20of%20mayors%20of%20Wichita%2C%20Kansas">Mayor</a> of <a href="Wichita%2C%20Kansas">Wichita, Kansas</a>. The election was held concurrently with various other local elections, and was officially nonpartisan. It saw the reelection of incumbent mayor <a href="Carl%20Brewer%20%28politician%29">Carl Brewer</a>.
